<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink330">
<l>ventuka ḷākiya veyiṟkaṭa nīnti</l>
<l>vantaṉa māyiṉu moḻikiṉic celavē</l>
<l>yaḻuta kaṇṇa ḷāynalañ citaiyak</l>
<l>katirteṟu veñcura niṉaikku</l>
<l>mavirkō lāytoṭi yuḷḷattup paṭarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Although we have come trudging through harsh paths </l>
<l>that have turned into hot dust in the heat, </l>
<l>now let us give up going further! </l>
<l>Affliction is in the mind of the girl [wearing] bright round choice bracelets, </l>
<l>who thinks about the hot desert, scorched by the sunrays, </l>
<l>and the excellent beauty of the girl with crying eyes perishes. </l>
        </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
